WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:02.041
… wife of a United Nations diplomat.

00:02.291 --> 00:03.333
She lives in London now

00:03.542 --> 00:05.750
but has thousands of followers around the world,

00:05.959 --> 00:08.875
who hail Her as India’s greatest living saint.

00:09.041 --> 00:12.375
She teaches a state of self-realization and happiness, and says

00:12.583 --> 00:16.291
that with a spiritual force She can cure the incurable.

00:16.542 --> 00:18.625
She’s speaking at public meetings in Bedford tonight

00:18.834 --> 00:20.125
and Northampton tomorrow,

00:20.333 --> 00:23.166
and today She gave Her first television interview in England.

00:23.375 --> 00:25.625
Our reporter is Rebecca (inaudible) .

00:26.375 --> 00:28.583
Her Holiness Mataji Nirmala Devi

00:28.792 --> 00:31.291
is known around the world for Her healing powers.

00:31.542 --> 00:33.959
Her followers look upon Her as Divine.

00:34.125 --> 00:37.667
Mother, as She is referred to, preaches a gospel of peace

00:37.875 --> 00:40.999
and has discovered a spiritual force called Kundalini,

00:41.166 --> 00:43.125
which is shown on this chart.

00:43.333 --> 00:45.875
She can release it in seekers, as She calls them,

00:46.041 --> 00:48.500
to give them complete awareness.

00:48.709 --> 00:51.792
She admits that many Westerners are sceptical of Her powers,

00:51.999 --> 00:54.959
but She scorns the idea of charging money for Her gifts.

00:55.125 --> 00:58.542
Her claims of success in curing and healing are remarkable.

00:58.750 --> 01:00.959
Alcoholics have been known to give up drink,

01:01.125 --> 01:04.917
drug-takers have been cured, but perhaps most extraordinary of all,

01:05.125 --> 01:07.917
She claims to have cured many cancer victims.

01:08.083 --> 01:11.208
REPORTER: How many people have you managed to cure who have had cancer?

01:11.417 --> 01:13.291
SHRI MATAJI: Thousands… I don’t know… I should say…

01:13.500 --> 01:17.583
REPORTER: Thousands? What do doctors think of what you’re saying?

01:17.834 --> 01:19.375
SHRI MATAJI: You see the trouble is

01:19.625 --> 01:24.041
I Myself I have done medicine and… the doctors are the people

01:24.250 --> 01:26.458
who are working with the “shoot” side of life, you see,

01:26.667 --> 01:28.166
not the “roots” of it.

01:28.375 --> 01:30.125
So the trouble with them is

01:30.333 --> 01:32.834
that anybody starts talking that it can be cured

01:33.000 --> 01:36.999
by a higher method than a human awareness,

01:37.166 --> 01:39.125
then they don’t want to jump into that awareness,

01:39.333 --> 01:42.250
which is a higher awareness that one has to achieve,

01:42.458 --> 01:45.125
because human awareness is still transitory.

01:45.333 --> 01:48.375
You have to achieve that awareness which is the divine awareness.

01:48.583 --> 01:51.667
When you have that awareness, then only you can cure it.

01:51.917 --> 01:53.458
REPORTER: How would You describe Yourself,

01:53.667 --> 01:56.500
as a healer or a spiritualist?

01:56.709 --> 02:00.333
SHRI MATAJI: You see, I do not want to fall into any category Myself

02:00.542 --> 02:04.125
because… I’m a housewife

02:04.333 --> 02:06.333
and I have to do all the jobs of a housewife,

02:06.542 --> 02:10.625
I’m also a diplomat’s wife, so I have to act as a diplomat’s wife,

02:10.834 --> 02:17.166
I’m also a person who has to do this work of Sahaja Yoga…

02:17.375 --> 02:20.083
So I don’t know how to describe Myself.

02:20.333 --> 02:22.083
REPORTER: Can I ask You if You can reach me?

02:22.291 --> 02:24.542
SHRI MATAJI: Yes yes, see, one can reach masses.

02:24.750 --> 02:29.417
Now, we have to first see in your case now what is the problem.

02:29.625 --> 02:32.500
First is that there’s an imbalance, a little imbalance,

02:32.709 --> 02:35.125
because you have to work outside too much, I think,

02:35.333 --> 02:37.208
you have to go out too much

02:37.417 --> 02:40.208
and don’t have much time for your emotional life.

02:40.417 --> 02:43.999
So it’s more that you are more mental and physical,

02:44.166 --> 02:47.166
but less of emotions in you, so there has to be a balance.

02:47.375 --> 02:50.917
So first I have to give a balance like this, all right?

02:51.166 --> 02:53.166
I have to put you into balance now.

02:53.417 --> 02:56.709
Now, this is, you are working with your mind too much,

02:56.917 --> 03:00.625
so you are over-working it, so your liver is out.

03:00.875 --> 03:03.458
And the liver is also excited.

03:03.667 --> 03:08.875
So to put it right what we have to do is to just put you…

03:09.250 --> 03:10.417
REPORTER: What are you doing?

03:10.625 --> 03:12.625
SHRI MATAJI: Just I’m removing the liver pressure.

03:12.834 --> 03:17.125
The liver is expressed in this part and this part of the hand.

03:17.333 --> 03:20.875
So your liver pressure is reduced. It’s very simple.

03:21.083 --> 03:22.542
REPORTER: Now, is anyone watching this

03:22.750 --> 03:24.959
going to have, feel any effect from You?

03:25.166 --> 03:26.208
SHRI MATAJI: From Me? REP: Yes.

03:26.417 --> 03:28.542
SHRI MATAJI: No no, no effect. No, nothing.

03:28.750 --> 03:30.000
Because it is just, you see,

03:30.208 --> 03:32.750
it’s like construction of the destruction;

03:32.959 --> 03:33.667
you just take out

03:33.875 --> 03:36.458
the destruction out of the construction, that’s all.

03:36.667 --> 03:39.875
It’s very simple. Now, what I am doing now.

03:40.041 --> 03:41.458
You have to now just say

03:41.667 --> 03:43.750
within yourself — or loudly if you want to —

03:43.959 --> 03:48.542
say that “Mother, I forgive everyone.” Just say that.

03:48.792 --> 03:50.041
REPORTER: Mother, I forgive everyone.

03:50.250 --> 03:52.625
SHRI MATAJI: Yes, you have to say thrice. Now let’s see. Say it.

03:52.834 --> 03:54.959
REPORTER: Mother, I forgive everyone. SHRI MATAJI: Again.

03:55.125 --> 03:57.166
REPORTER: Mother, I forgive everyone. SHRI MATAJI: Again.

03:57.375 --> 03:59.166
REPORTER: Mother, I forgive everyone.

03:59.375 --> 04:02.000
SHRI MATAJI: Now see.

04:02.250 --> 04:05.625
Is it flowing? A little bit.

04:05.834 --> 04:09.375
It’s very sensitive, it’s very subtle.

04:11.375 --> 04:14.333
REPORTER: Well, I can… I can feel the clearness of it. Yes.

04:14.542 --> 04:17.083
SHRI MATAJI: It’s started. Started, see?

04:17.291 --> 04:19.709
Just I… what I’m making — a cross on your hand.

04:19.917 --> 04:22.999
You see, that’s Christ, who said you have to forgive.

04:23.208 --> 04:25.500
Now see. It’s working?

04:25.792 --> 04:27.792
REPORTER: And what will it do for me in the long run?

04:27.999 --> 04:29.458
SHRI MATAJI: In the... in the long run that it is your…

04:29.709 --> 04:32.041
own power now will manifest.

04:32.250 --> 04:33.792
You have this power within yourself.

04:33.999 --> 04:36.667
Now with this you will feel very peaceful,

04:36.917 --> 04:38.208
you will

04:38.542 --> 04:40.208
control your thoughts. You don`t have to think

04:40.458 --> 04:42.083
all the time. You can rest without thinking.

04:42.333 --> 04:45.125
If you want you can think, otherwise you need not think.

04:45.333 --> 04:47.291
Then your own powers will be manifested,

04:47.500 --> 04:49.208
by which you can give this power to others.

04:49.417 --> 04:51.709
There’s so many things you can do.
